=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 12, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xlf1665702534189.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xlf1665702534189.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xlf1665702534189.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xlf1665702534189\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get the specified view of the component instance.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xlf1665702534189__topic_d125696e1_d125697e1_d125698e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xlf1665702534189__p_d125699e1_d125700e1_d125701e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentInstance</var>.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getView</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(<var class=\"keyword varname\">ViewName</var>)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xlf1665702534189__section_sxb_kgr_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d180750e73\">Arguments</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"xlf1665702534189__parml_h3v_mgr_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">ViewName</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the required View.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xlf1665702534189__section_prk_kgr_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d180750e91\">Return Value</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"xlf1665702534189__parml_kdk_rgr_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Return</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\"><span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.View</span> object representing the specified view. If the View\n            does not exist or is not valid, returns <code class=\"ph codeph\">null</code>.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xlf1665702534189__section_kvt_cn5_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d180750e114\">Example: Creating and Addressing Views</h2>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xlf1665702534189_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xlf1665702534189__codeblock_a5j_5gr_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">// creating a view\nmyInstance.createView(\"myView\", \"../myapp/view1.html\", document.getElementById('mydiv')).then(function (view) {\n // view is created and ready\n});\n// getting a view \nvar view = myInstance.getView(\"myview\"); \n// showing a view\nmyInstance.getView(\"myview\").show(\"body\").then(function () {\n // view is now shown and realized\n});</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtg1665702533539.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Instance</a><p>The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xbg1665702534713.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.View</a><p>The uniface.View object represents a view of a component that has been created by calling instance.createView().</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/skz1665702535167.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Multiple Views for Dynamic Server Pages</a><p>A View is an HTML layout that is displayed inside an unbound HTML element in the layout of the web page. Each instance of a dynamic server page (DSP) can have multiple views that provide different layouts for its data.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533769\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533769\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "getView() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 12, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get the specified view of the component instance. Return = ComponentInstance . getView ( ViewName ) Arguments ViewName Name of the required View. Return Value Return uniface.View object representing the specified view. If the View does not exist or is not valid, returns null . Example: Creating and Addressing Views Explain this code // creating a view myInstance.createView(\"myView\", \"../myapp/view1.html\", document.getElementById('mydiv')).then(function (view) { // view is created and ready }); // getting a view var view = myInstance.getView(\"myview\"); // showing a view myInstance.getView(\"myview\").show(\"body\").then(function () { // view is now shown and realized }); Copy Related Links uniface.Instance The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents. uniface.View The uniface.View object represents a view of a component that has been created by calling instance.createView(). Multiple Views for Dynamic Server Pages A View is an HTML layout that is displayed inside an unbound HTML element in the layout of the web page. Each instance of a dynamic server page (DSP) can have multiple views that provide different layouts for its data. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}